{"tid":1051482,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"同兩老去曼谷 有咩好做","createTime":"2019-03-07T15:41:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T13:44:43.000Z","uid":76611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3d9aa93c951bb217479a9b60cb4b1a53000e1238","tid":1051482,"uid":76611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T15:41:12.000Z","msg":"因為asia miles就到期 日本機票搵極都係waiting<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以打算求其篤同兩老5月中去曼谷<br />\n好耐之前老母跟團去過一次 老豆就未去過<br />\n諗緊去5日4夜定短短地4日3夜算<br />\n我近呢兩年每年都會同fd去一次曼谷<br />\n但都係市中心入面鳩hea鳩行揼下骨 夜晚去night market<br />\n同兩老去初步望過下可能都係join啲1 day tour<br />\n去動物園 鐵道市場或者水上市場嗰啲<br />\n真係冇乜idea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人提議下如果同兩老去可以做啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7e421957c15d4d7e8b4d75ab03a2f766e258ab9","tid":1051482,"uid":240455,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T15:46:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"776b0d3f1b5bc6fee73f6f7ea9397eee0aeb77e9","tid":1051482,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T15:54:08.000Z","msg":"喺resort週邊玩幾日"},{"pid":"dcd75ff5ec6644c475cc482d635b271bc5737979","tid":1051482,"uid":114692,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T15:59:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f48d83b55a43be6967a377446d7dbdb5b184851","tid":1051482,"uid":76611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7e421957c15d4d7e8b4d75ab03a2f766e258ab9","tid":1051482,"uid":240455,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3d9aa93c951bb217479a9b60cb4b1a53000e1238","tid":1051482,"uid":76611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T15:41:12.000Z","msg":"因為asia miles就到期 日本機票搵極都係waiting<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以打算求其篤同兩老5月中去曼谷<br />\n好耐之前老母跟團去過一次 老豆就未去過<br />\n諗緊去5日4夜定短短地4日3夜算<br />\n我近呢兩年每年都會同fd去一次曼谷<br />\n但都係市中心入面鳩hea鳩行揼下骨 夜晚去night market